org.osgi.service.http.whiteboard.propertytypes

Annotation Type HttpWhiteboardServletName


  • @ComponentPropertyType
 @Retention(value=CLASS)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @RequireHttpWhiteboard
public @interface HttpWhiteboardServletName
    Component Property Type for the osgi.http.whiteboard.servlet.name service property.

    This annotation can be used on a Servlet to declare the value of the HTTP_WHITEBOARD_SERVLET_NAME service property.

    Since:
    1.1
    See Also:
    "Component Property Types"
